    <item>
      <title>中国电动汽车制造商在曼谷车展上亮相，推出新车型</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-ev-makers-take-centre-stage-bangkok-motor-show-unveil-new-models-2024-03-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受强劲电动汽车销量的推动，中国汽车制造商将在本周的曼谷国际汽车展上成为众人瞩目的焦点，突显出长期主导泰国汽车市场的日本汽车巨头面临的日益严峻的挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-ev-makers-take-centre-stage-bangkok-motor-show-unveil-new-models-2024-03-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 07:13:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日产计划到 2027 年推出 30 款新车型，提升全球销量</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/nissan-targets-1-mln-vehicle-sales-growth-over-next-three-years-2024-03-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日产汽车周一表示，将在未来三年内推出 30 款新车型，目标是将全球销量增加 100 万辆，同时削减成本以提高盈利能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/nissan-targets-1-mln-vehicle-sales-growth-over-next-three-years-2024-03-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 06:26:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>数据显示，亚洲私募股权交易第一季度将创 2015 年以来最差水平</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/asia-private-equity-deals-set-worst-q1-since-2015-data-shows-2024-03-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[数据显示，由于中国交易停滞以及更广泛的经济和地缘政治不确定性拖累市场情绪，亚洲私募股权支持的并购活动将迎来近十年来最糟糕的开局。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/asia-private-equity-deals-set-worst-q1-since-2015-data-shows-2024-03-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 05:02:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新交所将披露第三季度大宗商品交易商头寸</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/sgx-disclose-trader-positions-commodities-q3-2024-03-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新交所集团计划从第三季度开始每周披露铁矿石、橡胶和货运等大宗商品的交易头寸，以随着更多亚洲以外的交易商参与市场而提高透明度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/sgx-disclose-trader-positions-commodities-q3-2024-03-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 04:52:27 GMT</pubDate>
